PackageType classification logic:

hasData  hasVoice  hasSms  isUnlimited  →  PackageType
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  ✓        ✗         ✗        any       →  DATA_ONLY
  ✗        ✓         ✗        any       →  VOICE_ONLY
  ✗        ✗         ✓        any       →  TEXT_ONLY
  ✓        ✗         ✓        any       →  DATA_WITH_TEXT
  ✓        ✓         ✗        any       →  DATA_WITH_CALL
  ✗        ✓         ✓        any       →  TEXT_WITH_CALL
  ✓        ✓         ✓        ✓         →  DATA_WITH_ALL_UNLIMITED
  ✓        ✓         ✓        ✗         →  ALL_INCLUSIVE

Copy
ScopeType classification logic:

countries[]  →  map each to region via country-regions.ts  →  count unique regions

1 country                          →  LOCAL
2-15 countries, 1 region           →  REGIONAL
2-15 countries, 2+ regions         →  MULTI_COUNTRY
16+ countries                      →  GLOBAL

