Step 5: Query Flow
User requests GET /packages?packageType=DATA_WITH_ALL_UNLIMITED&scopeType=REGIONAL&countries=FR:

Request
  │
  ▼
PackagesService.searchPackages()
  │
  ├── 1. Query local DB first (pre-classified, fast)
  │     WHERE packageType = 'DATA_WITH_ALL_UNLIMITED'
  │       AND scopeType = 'REGIONAL'
  │       AND 'FR' = ANY(countries)
  │       AND isActive = true
  │
  ├── 2. If DB has results → apply pricing engine → return
  │
  └── 3. If DB empty → fall back to live fan-out
        ├── Fan out to all healthy providers
        ├── Each adapter maps + classifies on the fly
        ├── Filter results by packageType/scopeType in memory
        └── Apply pricing → return

